data.description: A charming and inviting single-family home nestled in a peaceful neighborhood of Fort Worth. Located in highly sought after Ridglea Hills Elementary School Area. This beautiful property offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless elegance. The home boasts an eye-catching curb appeal with a well-maintained front yard, lush greenery, and a welcoming covered patio, where you can relax and enjoy the tranquil surroundings. The exterior features a tasteful combination of brick and siding, adding to the home's classic charm, an ideal place to call home. Foundation work was recently completed.
